latestPosts.caption:
My body isn’t magazine perfect, but when I look in the mirror I see a mother of two cute little monsters 👿 and there is no great honour,love and blessings… 
My stretch marks, my loose sagging tummy are my strength and motivation which helps me to workout everyday…..☺️
I exercise because somehow completely exhausting myself is the most relaxing part of my day…. Taking care of yourself is a part of taking care of your kids…… I believe a baby is a reason and not an excuse…that’s why even after my second baby I came back like this within just 10months of postpartum 
Fit Moms don’t have time they make out 💪👍
But yes at the end of the day what I achieve is everyday my son look up to me and say that I want to become fit like you mom ❤️

#fitmom #fitnessjourney #boymom #postpartumjourney #postpartumfitness #selflove #blessed #selfcare #exercise #motherlove #instagram #instamommy #instafit #instamood
